00:31:30,867 --> 00:31:32,900
People were going
back to the beginning.

523
00:31:32,900 --> 00:31:35,933
They were peering into new
dimensions of space and time,

524
00:31:35,933 --> 00:31:38,333
looking for positive
proof of evolution.

525
00:31:38,333 --> 00:31:39,867
The origins of man.

526
00:31:40,433 --> 00:31:42,567
The mythic stories
from ancient Greece.

527
00:31:42,567 --> 00:31:44,000
It spread like wildfire,

528
00:31:44,000 --> 00:31:46,233
and it formed civilization
as we know it.

529
00:31:47,400 --> 00:31:50,367
- If this techology existed,
we could learn everything.

530
00:31:50,367 --> 00:31:51,567
- Everything.

531
00:31:52,300 --> 00:31:54,133
- I mean, think of
what we could do.

532
00:31:54,133 --> 00:31:56,233
What we could
accomplish with that.

533
00:31:56,233 --> 00:31:57,900
- Oh, the things we
could accomplish.

534
00:31:59,267 --> 00:32:01,300
I used to think like
that when I was your age.

