00:32:16,967 --> 00:32:18,767
we were never meant to see.

541
00:32:19,467 --> 00:32:21,967
Some, including myself, argued

542
00:32:21,967 --> 00:32:25,300
that human progression was
as natural as time itself.

543
00:32:26,267 --> 00:32:27,767
So we proceded.

544
00:32:28,667 --> 00:32:31,967
All of society's mysteries and
questions could be answered.

545
00:32:34,900 --> 00:32:36,500
I spent so much
time concentrating

546
00:32:36,500 --> 00:32:38,000
on the fallout
from travel that I

547
00:32:38,000 --> 00:32:40,733
never considered the
ramifications of viewing.

