00:32:45,700 --> 00:32:47,600
Why are the Kennedys
being killed?

551
00:32:48,033 --> 00:32:49,633
Two brothers, a son.

552
00:32:51,000 --> 00:32:53,067
Scholars would look back
at the savage nature

553
00:32:53,067 --> 00:32:55,467
of European settlers
who stole the country

554
00:32:55,467 --> 00:32:56,867
from Native Americans.

555
00:32:58,067 --> 00:32:59,700
The truth divided us.

556
00:33:00,233 --> 00:33:02,100
And individually armed us.

557
00:33:03,500 --> 00:33:06,467
The world lost faith not just
in God, but in everything.

558
00:33:07,700 --> 00:33:10,733
Anarchy replaced order.

559
00:33:11,367 --> 00:33:14,267
Crime, corruption,
destruction took over.

560
00:33:14,267 --> 00:33:16,467
No one was afraid
of anything anymore.

561
00:33:17,900 --> 00:33:19,133
No more questions.

562
00:33:19,600 --> 00:33:20,967
No more beliefs.

563
00:33:21,700 --> 00:33:24,433
And all because I couldn't
see down that road.

564
00:33:31,700 --> 00:33:33,100
- Time viewing, huh?

565
00:33:35,633 --> 00:33:38,000
But you're not actually
viewing me, you're here.

566
00:33:38,900 --> 00:33:42,600
You're actually sitting right
here, so how is that possible?

567
00:33:43,533 --> 00:33:44,700
- You don't believe me?

568
00:33:44,700 --> 00:33:45,700
- It's not my job
to believe you,

569
00:33:45,700 --> 00:33:47,067
but I wanna understand.

570
00:33:47,067 --> 00:33:49,867
So, so, okay, so
you created this

571
00:33:49,867 --> 00:33:51,767
amazing technology but not now,

572
00:33:51,767 --> 00:33:53,000
some time in the future.

