00:36:54,300 --> 00:36:55,467
- What?

641
00:36:56,133 --> 00:36:58,133
- What if originally
Hitler was killed?

642
00:36:59,200 --> 00:37:00,867
And someone went
back and changed it?

643
00:37:01,733 --> 00:37:02,900
Kept him alive.

644
00:37:04,233 --> 00:37:06,900
To us, we would remember
it as our history.

645
00:37:07,767 --> 00:37:09,500
As if it always happened.

646
00:37:09,500 --> 00:37:12,533
Many people believe that time
eventually corrects itself.

647
00:37:13,700 --> 00:37:15,467
If Hitler was dead,
someone would likely

648
00:37:15,467 --> 00:37:17,233
step up and take his place.

