00:37:17,900 --> 00:37:20,200
Thank God, mercifully I've
never had to test that theory.

650
00:37:24,000 --> 00:37:24,933
- Yeah, but you can.

651
00:37:27,867 --> 00:37:29,067
- I guess so.

652
00:37:29,067 --> 00:37:30,667
- You being here brings
all that into question.

653
00:37:33,700 --> 00:37:34,933
I gotta drink, man.

654
00:37:37,067 --> 00:37:39,667
You want a soda, a
scotch, water, what?

655
00:37:39,667 --> 00:37:41,200
- Glass of water'll
be great, Doc.

