00:38:19,667 --> 00:38:21,133
I think regardless
of what happens now

664
00:38:21,133 --> 00:38:22,900
there'll always
be that curiosity.

665
00:38:23,367 --> 00:38:26,133
I can safely say I've never
seen anything like this before.

666
00:38:27,367 --> 00:38:28,267
- Good.

667
00:38:28,867 --> 00:38:30,300
That's all I could hope for.

668
00:38:30,300 --> 00:38:32,333
- Guess what I still don't
understand is how you're here.

669
00:38:33,100 --> 00:38:34,867
Or if there's some other
reason why you're here.

670
00:38:35,600 --> 00:38:36,900
Is there?

671
00:38:36,900 --> 00:38:38,433
- It's all about causality.

672
00:38:38,433 --> 00:38:41,600
The only remaining question
