00:38:51,567 --> 00:38:53,700
But I know if I didn't
try and talk to somebody

677
00:38:53,700 --> 00:38:55,467
about what I know, it would add

678
00:38:55,467 --> 00:38:58,600
to the long line of regrets
that I keep with me.

679
00:38:59,233 --> 00:39:01,567
Maybe fate does exist,
and maybe it doesn't.

680
00:39:02,267 --> 00:39:04,867
Maybe it's our destiny to
live with mistakes I've made.

681
00:39:05,533 --> 00:39:07,600
Or it could be my
destiny to change them.

