00:39:24,267 --> 00:39:27,000
as a sane man would, but,

688
00:39:28,567 --> 00:39:30,467
with that being said I
still gotta know more.

689
00:39:34,067 --> 00:39:36,167
- Did you ever wish you
could change things?

690
00:39:36,167 --> 00:39:37,600
- Of course.

691
00:39:38,867 --> 00:39:40,400
I don't think you're ever
gonna be alone in that.

692
00:39:45,267 --> 00:39:47,767
- There was a time when I
lived to help other people.

693
00:39:48,467 --> 00:39:49,900
Like you're doing.

694
00:39:50,300 --> 00:39:53,233
