00:40:19,133 --> 00:40:22,000
- My friends, my family mainly.

706
00:40:24,267 --> 00:40:26,100
After a while I
pushed them away.

707
00:40:27,300 --> 00:40:28,567
But not by choice.

708
00:40:29,900 --> 00:40:31,200
- They didn't see what you did?

709
00:40:32,167 --> 00:40:34,800
- No, this time I didn't
see what they did.

710
00:40:35,500 --> 00:40:36,867
Who would've guessed
