00:41:49,500 --> 00:41:50,967
Or he pretended.

741
00:41:58,200 --> 00:41:59,400
- Something you wanna tell me?

742
00:42:02,867 --> 00:42:03,700
Jason?

743
00:42:04,867 --> 00:42:06,267
- Sorry, man, what's up?

744
00:42:07,767 --> 00:42:09,400
- What's on your mind, man?

745
00:42:10,333 --> 00:42:12,267
- I don't know if I can
