750
00:42:20,700 --> 00:42:21,933
What's going on?

751
00:42:23,633 --> 00:42:25,500
- I just really wasn't
prepared for today.

752
00:42:28,067 --> 00:42:30,200
This old patient of mine
came in off the street.

753
00:42:31,067 --> 00:42:32,167
We'd been talking
for about a year,

754
00:42:32,167 --> 00:42:33,200
I didn't think anything of it.

755
00:42:33,200 --> 00:42:34,900
I mean he's a normal enough guy.

756
00:42:34,900 --> 00:42:36,700
I mean, you know, normal
in a certain light,

