00:43:30,000 --> 00:43:31,733
That's why I brought
that thing up before.

780
00:43:33,200 --> 00:43:34,733
I just wanted to know
what you would do.

781
00:43:37,233 --> 00:43:38,700
- If the world gets
worse and worse

782
00:43:38,700 --> 00:43:41,667
over the next few years, then
I'd say we had it coming.

